### Create data mappings for index

curl -H "Content-Type: application/x-ndjson" -X PUT http://localhost:9200/game-rules -ku admin:admin --data-binary "@game-rules-field-mappings.json"

### Update data mappings for index

curl -H "Content-Type: application/x-ndjson" -X PUT http://localhost:9200/game-rules/_mapping -ku admin:admin --data-binary "@game-rules-field-mappings.json"

### Bulk load data

curl -H "Content-Type: application/x-ndjson" -X PUT http://localhost:9200/game-rules/_bulk -ku admin:admin --data-binary "@game-rules-data.json"

### Delete document

curl -X DELETE http://localhost:9200/game-rules/_doc/1 -ku admin:admin


### Delete index

curl -X DELETE http://localhost:9200/game-rules -ku admin:admin


